{"tid":235399,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會選舉被指「港獨」遭DQ　民族黨陳浩天選舉呈請今審","createTime":"2017-05-09T03:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T08:44:32.000Z","uid":92301,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a8923c28b9ec2b8b94ee95898c5ff69dbf1c04b","tid":235399,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/899085/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F899085%2F&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=3fbf4991\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F899085%2F&h=883bb0ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/899085/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gclhu9r5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgclhu9r5&h=d742e555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本於去年立法會選舉出選新界西的香港民族黨召集人陳浩天，因被指支持「港獨」而被取消資格，他指選舉主任剝奪基本法列明港人擁有的選舉權及被選舉權，高院今就他提出的選舉呈請進行審訊。<br />\n<br />\n代表陳浩天的資深大律師李志喜指，陳簽署的聲明已經列明他確認閱讀及明白基本法內容，選舉主任無權透過其過往言論，決定參選人有否真誠擁護基本法，是否符合參選資格。"},{"pid":"271d07dc8410b68d482704a81ccd181b0add4e9a","tid":235399,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:51:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=938932&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D938932%26csid%3D261_341&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=f90b78c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=938932&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n陳浩天選舉呈請案早上審理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g15sqpr3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg15sqpr3&h=6cf0491b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天，去年被取消立法會新界西選區的參選資格後，提出選舉呈請，要求法庭宣告選舉無效，案件早上在高等法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n呈請申請書指，選舉主任曾透過電郵查問陳浩天，是否仍推動香港獨立，超越條例賦予選舉主任的權力，選舉主任亦考慮了陳浩天的公開言論和政綱等不相關、及法律沒容許考慮的資料， 而決定取消他的資格。"},{"pid":"f1a2095fef06b1d684050e6ed654043b70b68f5b","tid":235399,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=938972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D938972&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=52b0be34\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=938972</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">陳浩天一方指政府不應篩選立法會候選人</span><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天，去年被取消立法會新界西選區的參選資格後，提出選舉呈請，要求法庭宣告選舉無效，案件早上在高等法院審理。代表陳浩天的資深大律師李志喜陳詞指，案件關鍵是參選立法會的資格和選舉主任的權力。她說選舉主任只需因應參選人年齡、提名等條件判斷，不應由政府進行篩選，亦不應該判斷參選人，簽署擁護基本法聲明的目的，否則會削弱選擇制度。她又說選舉主任拒絕披露根據甚麼法律意見，而詢問陳浩天的政治立場，並取消他的參選資格，陳浩天並非拒絕回答選舉主任有關他政治立場的查詢，而是需要知道背後的理據再作考慮。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天一方又指，參選立法會需擁護基本法，但不代表要認同每一條條文，並完全不作更改。"},{"pid":"8aec686454df19925b0e200ed9849f0b5de81e9c","tid":235399,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=758727664301593&amp;id=396949433812753\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D758727664301593%26id%3D396949433812753&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=2cc871f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=758727664301593&amp;id=396949433812753</a><br />\n<br />\nChung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰：陳浩天選舉呈請案，相關的現任議員只有我一個到庭聽審。"},{"pid":"26fbd56b5331d966838cb0d186bf63a08301f48d","tid":235399,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9eef96d817e570035849c829174a7963afb52a","